Ranger Help for: balance weapon
================================

SYNTAX:      balance <weapon>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   4
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to carefully adjust the balance of a weapon,
improving its accuracy in combat. The weapon must be non-magical for
the Ranger to work with it. The degree of improvement depends on the
Ranger's skill level and dexterity. A well-balanced weapon can make
the difference between a hit and a miss in the heat of battle.
